Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory261.png'}
{3: "It has been a week since you agreed to be Leonie's test subject for Hamlet Gen-2."}
{3: "During this week, Leonie's mental state has noticeably taken a great turn."}
{3: "From which you've learned that it would only take 147 consecutive error alerts for a person's great passion to rapidly dissipate into despair."}
{1: '999', 2: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory101.png', 3: '0', 4: '1', 5: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory101.png'}
{3: "After knocking on the WGAA's door once more, you are greeted with an unexpected figure inside."}
{3: "Constructs don't develop dark circles under their eyes, but the tone of her greeting reveals the all-nighters she has pulled recently."}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: "Living your cozy life, aren't you, 【kuroname】?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Vanessa?', 3: '18', 4: 'What brings you here?', 5: '18'}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: "You're late.", 4: '2'}
{2: "I'm five minutes earlier than the scheduled time."}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: "You're wrong, because I pushed the start of the test ten minutes earlier.", 4: '2'}
{2: "...You're also here to be a tester?", 3: '23', 4: "You're sure taking over fast.", 5: '24'}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: 'To be the tester "lead."', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: "Utilizing someone with exceptional leadership skills would be the wise choice, wouldn't you agree?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Leonie', 3: "Hm? You two are not on good terms? But I remember you're listed as peer commandants.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Leonie', 3: 'Sica also mentioned to me a senior who taught her a lot after graduation. She was speaking with a lot of respect.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Leonie', 3: "Vanessa reached out to me a few days ago, saying that she wanted to help. That's very kind-hearted of her, don't you think?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kind-hearted...', 4: "You're probably the first one to describe her with that word."}
{2: 'Leonie', 3: 'Well... putting that aside, I do need more sample data for reference.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Leonie', 3: 'Commandant Vanessa has shown a remarkably high level of Mind Beacon strength, and so far, there have been no observed adverse reactions in her previous tests.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Leonie', 3: "She has even gone as far as helping me create test plans that account for various variables, which I'm probably gonna stick with.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: 'Alright, chit-chat time is over.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: '【kuroname】, your opponent is me this time.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Vanessa', 3: 'Make sure you cooperate with my test, got it?', 4: '2'}
